'''Upsilon''' was a letter in the [[Tionese/Legends|Tionese alphabet]]. Upsilon was often used as a call sign for [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Starship/Legends|starships]], often [[Transport/Legends|transports]] such as the [[Lambda-class T-4a shuttle/Legends|''Lambda''-class shuttle]]. Shuttle ''Upsilon 2'' was one such example.

